\b Service Log Capture - Architecture\b0\par
Complaint Management System\par
\par

\b 1. Purpose\b0\par
Service Log Capture records service visits against an Installed Base machine. It stores service details, visit dates, serial number, complaint link, and part replacements. Spare Parts records can be added from a Service Log.\par
\par

\b 2. Main Files\b0\par
\bullet  service_log.php - list, add/edit form, grid actions\par
\bullet  service_log_details.php - view one record\par
\bullet  delete_service_log.php - delete record\par
\bullet  includes/service_log_helpers.php - validation and save logic\par
\bullet  api/service_log_datatable.php - grid data\par
\bullet  api/service_log_get.php - edit data\par
\bullet  api/service_log_create.php / service_log_update.php - create and update\par
\par

\b 3. Shared Components\b0\par
\bullet  installed_base_helpers.php / service_log_installed_base_select2.js - link to Installed Base\par
\bullet  service_log_part_replacement.js - part replacement rows\par
\bullet  installed_base_service_log_modal.php - add Service Log from Installed Base\par
\bullet  complaint_service_log_modal.php - add Service Log from Assign Complaint\par
\bullet  rbac_access_helpers.php - permissions\par
\bullet  after_market_access_helpers.php - user record access\par
\par

\b 4. Basic Flow\b0\par
\bullet  User opens Service Log Capture page\par
\bullet  Grid loads records from service_logs table\par
\bullet  User adds or edits a record and links Installed Base\par
\bullet  Optional part replacements are saved with the log\par
\bullet  Record is saved to service_logs\par
\bullet  From grid, user can add Spare Parts for a Service Log\par
\bullet  Also opened from Installed Base grid or Assign Complaint Service Update\par
\par

\b 5. Database\b0\par
Main table: service_logs\par
Related tables: service_log_part_replacements, installed_base, complaints, spare_parts_consumption\par
\par

\b 6. Permissions\b0\par
RBAC module: service-log-capture (view, add, edit, delete)\par
}
